2 actions

4 mana

touch range

2 tile effect AoE 

you do not place a rune on a surface to cast this spell.

first, make a spell attack against a creature within range. on a hit, they are stuck with a paper bomb which takes 1 full round to activate.

at the start of your next turn, you may detonate the bomb (timer is tracked seperate for each bomb if there are multiple). all active bombs are detonated simultaneously.

they deal 3d6 force damage to the stuck target, and nearby creatures must make either a focus check if they can see or sense your detonation, or an acrobatics check if they can see or sense the activation. if they cannot sense the detonation they automatically fail 

any creature who fails the check besides the stuck target takes 3d6 force damage.
